Fri Aug 10 21:08:28 UTC 2012  Adam Mitz  <mitza@ociweb.com>

        Integrated changes from Scott Harris and Tim Bradley:

        * dds/DCPS/transport/framework/RemoveAllVisitor.cpp:
        * dds/DCPS/transport/framework/TransportQueueElement.inl:

          msg_payload() and msg() methods of TransportQueueElement can return
          NULL pointers.  Especially in the case of msg_payload(), there are
          queue elements that have a header but no payload.

        * dds/DCPS/transport/framework/DataLink.cpp:

          handle_timeout() calls the new unbind_link() method on the transport,
          which allows the link to be removed from transport-specific data
          structures.  The rest of handle_timeout() was equivalent to stop().
          pre_stop_i() is now called from stop().

        * dds/DCPS/transport/framework/TransportImpl.h:
        * dds/DCPS/transport/framework/TransportImpl.cpp:
        * dds/DCPS/transport/tcp/TcpTransport.h:
